Movie Description
Wild Bill Hickok and Crazy Horse, two of the Wild West&#039;s most legendary figures, search for the fabled white beast...and their own salvation.

Credits 
Cast: Charles Bronson 
Director: J. Lee Thompson 

Synopsis
An aging Wild Bill Hickok finds his dreams haunted by an albino buffalo, which he believes symbolizes his own death. His preoccupation with the animal forces him to go west to hunt it down -- and perhaps come to terms with his own mortality in the process.
